# VARE — Voice Authenticity Risk Engine
# REST Client file — works in VS Code with "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
# Install: Extensions → search "REST Client" → Install
# Usage: Click "Send Request" above any request block

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8001

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Health Check
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

# Expected Response:
# HTTP/1.1 200 OK
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "device": "cpu",
#   "models_loaded": {
#     "aasist3": true,
#     "wav2vec2": true,
#     "rawnet2": false
#   }
# }


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. Analyze Audio File
# Replace the file path below with your audio file
# Supported: .wav .mp3 .flac .ogg .m4a .webm
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Analyze Audio
POST {{baseUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="audio.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< C:/Users/User/Downloads/audio.wav
--boundary--

