# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Risk Level Reference
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# ensemble_score   risk_level   meaning
# 0  – 30          LOW          Confident real / Genuine
# 31 – 60          MEDIUM       Suspicious, flag for review
# 61 – 100         HIGH         Strong AI / synthetic indicators
